===Pronunciation===
שׂישׂ -   שׂוּשׂ / śûś  śîyś / soos, sece

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''שׂוּשׂ'''

# To be bright, that is, cheerful: - be glad, X greatly, joy, make mirth, [[rejoice]].

